headline: How Will Fresh Analyst Optimism Amid Oversold Trading Shape Nasdaq's (NDAQ) Outlook?
summary: Nasdaq recently hosted its "Building the Future Summit 2025" in New York, and the Nasdaq Vilnius Stock Exchange listed Hotrema bonds on the First North market following a successful EUR 5 million raise in Lithuania. Analyst consensus has shifted as Nasdaq enters oversold territory, with increased optimism about stronger earnings prospects based on raised estimates and analyst agreement. We’ll explore how rising analyst optimism for improved earnings after recent selling pressure could...
